'Kamu akan aman
jika kamu tetap diam.'

00:27:37.120 --> 00:27:39.160 line:20%
'Akan berbahaya bagimu
jika kamu berbicara.'

00:27:49.440 --> 00:27:53.040 line:20%
'Aku harus melalui
banyak hal karenamu.'

00:27:53.600 --> 00:27:55.440 line:20%
'Saya harus mentolerir penghinaan'

00:27:55.520 --> 00:27:58.160 line:20%
'kemarahan orang-orang,
ejekan dan segalanya.'

00:27:58.400 --> 00:28:00.280 line:20%
'Kamu..
- Hei!  Bergerak!'

00:28:01.960 --> 00:28:02.920 line:20%
'Anu!'